### Create a Payment
POST {{baseAddress}}/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{passwordToken}}
{
  "OrderCode": "6657c883-2e9b-43e4-a421-45f9ef25b415",
